contentfulProduct.name: Salmon & Rice Paté
contentfulProduct.teaser: Salmon and Rice Paté, low-grain, complete and balanced wetfood for adult dogs

ingredients.ingredients: 57% Fresh meat and meat products(min.8% lamb), fresh salmon 25%, rice 4%, herbal products, minerals.

analysis.analysis: Protein 7.5%, fat content 4%, crude ash 2.5%,crude fibre 0.4%, moisture 82%.

feedingRecommendation.feedingRecommendation: Freshwater should always be available. Prior to opening the pack,  it should be stored in dry, cool conditions. After opening, store in an airtight container, keep refrigerated and use it within 72 Hours. The recommended quantities can vary according to breed, seasonal and age factors. Traceability: Best before date/lot no, see can bottom.

nutritionAdditives.nutritionAdditives: Vitamin A 750 IU/kg, Vitamin D3 75IU/kg , Vitamin E 10IU/kg, Zinc (Zinc Sulphate Monohydrate) 3.8 mg/kg, Manganese (Manganous Sulphate Monohydrate) 1.9mg/kg, Selenium (Sodium Selenite) 0.02 mg/kg, Iodine (Calcium iodate anhydrous) 0.19 mg/kg.

longDescription.longDescription:
Chef’s Choice Salmon and Rice recipe for Adult Dogs is formulated by chefs and nutritionists, made with 100% fresh salmon and natural ingredients while having low-grain, and being free from sugar, salt, artificial colors, aromas or preservatives. This delicious and nutritious recipe is enhanced with vitamins, minerals and other nutrients to make your dog crave for more! 
You might be cooking your own food but your dog has a Chef at home.
